<bibRefCitation author="Polhemus" box="[803,998,1340,1364]" firstAuthor="Polhemus" pageId="24" pageNumber="25" refId="ref41836" refString="Polhemus, D. A. (1997) Systematics of the Genus Rhagovelia Mayr (Heteroptera: Veliidae) in the Western Hemisphere (Exclusive of the angustipes Complex). Entomological Society of America, Langham, 386 pp." type="book" year="1997">Polhemus (1997)</bibRefCitation>
, but without an indication of a collecting locality. No other references recording the species from the country were found, but considering its general distribution, it is more likely to occur in North and/or Central-West regions.
